Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:41.38,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been 32 years since the start\Nof the Tokugawa Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:44.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,lemitsu, the third Shogun,\Nnow rules a seemingly peaceful nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:49.42,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There remain, however,\Nnumerous problems still left unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:56.53,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Many forces are seeking to overthrow\Nthe Tokugawa government...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:59.96,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,and another cause for concern\Nis the clandestine Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:04.87,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that the clandestine\NChristians have a meeting tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:07.36,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're certain, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:45.47,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!\NCapture this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:26.05,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! Ring the bell!\NWe must warn the Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.13,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:46.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an overgrown tiger\Nthat's escaped from a freak show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.06,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.08,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We must protect the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.56,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.00,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.46,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.68,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:03.68,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.12,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:15.69,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.63,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, sir!\NThe thing is a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.60,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,- There is nothing we can do to stop it!\N- Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:26.07,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heading in the direction of\NEdo Castle! We must protect our Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:31.17,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! If I must give my life\Nto save the Lord, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.93,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:50.02,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir! You have saved\Nour Lord from this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.25,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.27,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:07.20,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the crest of two scythes\Ncrossing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:10.21,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's known as the "Scythes Of Death,"\Nsir, and is rarely used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:14.68,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be quite easy to find out\Nwho that man is, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.95,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll up! Roll up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.58,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and see\Nthe amazing snake woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:31.56,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,A snake that's lived\Nfor 200 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:36.69,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never have seen anything\Nso strange as the amazing snake woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:46.91,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That tiger broke out of its cage\Nand killed 50 police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wish it could've\Neaten my wife, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.85,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife? Nah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.45,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a tiger\Nwould be hungry enough to eat HER!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.66,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.33,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.23,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.36,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You bear the crest\Nof crossed scythes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:20.16,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Shuranosuke Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.13,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.80,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have orders to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.98,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:36.28,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you wish to stay alive,\Ndon't draw your swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.95,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:08.49,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.96,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:16.88,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Six men down in a single instant.\NIt's more than I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:21.86,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, these men were sacrificed\Nto test my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NThey were loyal servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:29.77,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I suppose\Nyou're a loyal servant, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:34.74,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunbei Tashiro, of the Nakura clan.\NI have my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:49.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been taught by Master Katori\Nin the Divine Shinto style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:56.03,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no master. I know no god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.97,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.97,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I deserve\Nsome explanation for all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.84,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,After our bout is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not be alive to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The silent blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.25,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Phantom."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.53,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Phantom," you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.50,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So brief is human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.68,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki! Sir! Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.36,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who slew a killer tiger\Nin a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:11:00.76,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had my men look all over Edo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:04.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,for the man bearing\Nthe "Scythes of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:08.63,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Daizen Imura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:16.31,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in charge of overseeing\Nthe affairs of the Nakura clan in Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.78,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders in the house! Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something\Nwe must ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.69,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiger was probably used\Nas a decoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:36.76,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,to draw the guards away\Nfrom the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.10,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The intruders succeeded\Nin taking her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.14,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:57.08,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess will be\Nreturned safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.42,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for the Ginryu Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:04.52,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Send one man to bring the sword\Nto the Benten Shrine in Ueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow night\Nat the hour of the Boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:11.19,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If our demand is not met,\Nthe Princess will be raped and killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,and her body will be exposed\Nfor all to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:15.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seki Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.10,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seki Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:26.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The notorious group of Ninja\Nthat served Motonari Mohri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:30.32,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately there is no one\Nin the Nakura clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:34.55,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,who can fight them single-handedly\Nto rescue the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:43.03,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Sakaki!\NSave our Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.22,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back early today,\NShuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:06.45,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one year's\Nadvance payment of the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.92,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Business is booming, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.59,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Petty job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:18.90,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.67,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:29.24,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:36.42,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.22,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha. That crest on your kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.62,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Scythe of Death" is considered\Nvery unlucky. It is rarely used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.83,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,A handsome fella wearing\Nthe "Scythe of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:50.33,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't too hard to find you,\NSakaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.30,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:57.83,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I want.\NEmbarrassing a girl in public like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.98,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems\NI've fallen in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.48,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Oren,\Nthe Kishibojin Goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.32,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I got my nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.26,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.77,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You do more than\Nkill tigers, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.97,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me so much\Nthat you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:08.67,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any man I sleep with\Nhas to be hateful, so coldhearted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:14.31,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,and so dangerous\Nthat he could kill me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.29,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oren, huh. I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:24.28,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven and hell\Nboth exist on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.20,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:37.54,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Sakaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:51.92,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, send me to hell\None more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.89,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.90,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise you might end up\Ngoing to hell for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.89,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seki Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.96,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:36.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill one, kill two,\Nit's the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:40.56,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a graveyard for lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:44.57,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What better place for you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.28,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.67,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Opium is made by drying\Nthe sap of poppies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:30.01,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been used over the years\Nas a sedative, and as a narcotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.65,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any order given\Nunder the influence of a drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.55,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,is said to have\Nstrong suggestive powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:40.08,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mizari cult\Nis known to have used drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.92,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,to control their assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:11.88,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ginryu Sword, the treasure\Nof the Sugawara household...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.25,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,is about to fall into the hands\Nof the Seki Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:18.63,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio. Pretty Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.59,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me the Ginryu Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:24.19,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Okuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.27,0:19:28.50,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will...\Nget you the Ginryu Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:53.72,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eikanji Temple\Nat Toueizan Mountain in Ueno...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:58.57,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,was built to ward off demons\Nfrom the Edo Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:06.01,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinobazu Pond is located on\Nthe southwest corner of Eikanji Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.98,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no bridges\Nto Benten Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:24.35,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Shuranosuke Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.55,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Dogan,\Nthe leader of the Seki Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.82,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you brought the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.26,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Princess Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.11,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Princess Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:58.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:01.52,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a hired hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:04.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:24.31,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. The Ginryu Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:30.54,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I figure it, you used\Nsome kind of drug to excite that tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:33.15,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And while all attention\Nwas focused on the tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:37.02,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,you kidnapped Princess Mayu,\Ndaughter of the Nakura clan leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:43.49,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why go through all this trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:46.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you so desire\Nthe Ginryu Sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:50.41,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like\Nan interesting enough tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.74,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,to tell over a bottle of sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:56.97,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. You won't be able\Nto drink sake in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:14.73,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill the boatkeeper\Nand his family?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:19.60,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No one sees the Seki Ninja\Nand lives to tell about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:22.47,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They were unlucky, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.44,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to kill the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:29.47,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whimpered like a pup\Nwhen I stabbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:35.05,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.42,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.79,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You louse. Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:29.44,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, Shuranosuke!\NThrow down your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.51,0:24:33.17,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let he go. I promised\Nto bring her home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.38,0:24:36.87,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be bringing back\Nher dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:39.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it, and the Nakura clan\Nwill also receive YOUR head...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.02,0:24:41.58,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,as a special gift from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.09,0:24:45.02,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.09,0:24:48.22,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?\NKill me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.53,0:24:53.52,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you answer\Njust one question, Sakaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.90,0:24:55.83,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:25:02.47,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is love? I shall die\Nwithout ever experiencing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.08,0:25:07.51,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is like the morning dew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.58,0:25:10.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It stays in this world\Nonly for a fleeting moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.41,0:25:13.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it does not even\Nbelong to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.39,0:25:19.59,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Now I am ready to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.66,0:25:23.65,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my head off, you lout!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.20,0:25:26.06,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.54,0:25:35.70,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, throw down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.77,0:25:38.30,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.32,0:25:52.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:25:58.35,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,After them! Kill them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:15.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.84,0:26:46.78,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?\NYou're not the Iga or Koga ninjas!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.01,0:26:49.74,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come for the Ginryu Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.36,0:27:38.12,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way, you monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.81,0:28:32.41,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kunoichi" (women) ninjas!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.48,0:28:36.65,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You must be the Himiko Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.90,0:28:50.77,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.68,0:29:02.15,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.21,0:29:04.20,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.28,0:29:07.55,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't call me\N"Dogan the Invincible" for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.41,0:29:38.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the Ginryu Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.53,0:29:55.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.58,0:30:16.45,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is heaven a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.19,0:30:20.95,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.03,0:30:24.08,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever think about dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.20,0:30:30.60,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is like the morning dew.\NIs human life like that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.00,0:30:33.30,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.34,0:30:41.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki! Shuranosuke Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.48,0:30:46.81,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been sent by the Nakura clan\Nto retrieve Princess Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.89,0:30:50.79,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take my hand, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.82,0:30:53.65,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.80,0:31:04.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.04,0:31:14.10,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.87,0:31:46.78,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Murakami! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.42,0:31:55.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinbei, Kota...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.02,0:31:57.85,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Koichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.92,0:32:00.62,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They all died for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.90,0:32:07.80,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.87,0:32:49.84,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Death is in the air tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.44,0:32:56.57,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of blood.\NMany lives have been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.38,0:33:00.37,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The streets of Edo\Ncan be dangerous at night, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.45,0:33:02.51,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must take caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.89,0:33:12.26,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer?\NHow much longer do we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.06,0:33:15.33,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little further, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.40,0:33:19.03,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been ordered to guide you\Nto Lord Tsusaka's mansion, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.10,0:33:20.26,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.34,0:33:23.27,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop here.\NThis seems like a good spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.34,0:33:28.78,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell of blood, too.\NThe blood of many men.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.65,0:33:34.11,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to hide\Nwho you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.18,0:33:39.28,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite confident\Nthat you can beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.36,0:33:42.38,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you wouldn't\Nturn your back to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.06,0:33:47.62,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsusaka must have\Nhired you to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:50.36,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be smart\Nto call the deal off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.43,0:33:54.93,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why waste your life\Nfor a no-good embezzler like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.51,0:33:58.50,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the offer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.58,0:34:01.01,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,it's my policy to carry out\Nany contract to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.08,0:34:03.84,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd even kill my own brother\Nif it came down to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:05.67,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.75,0:34:09.65,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I might not be the one\Nto end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.03,0:34:20.16,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma Utsuki. Superintendent officer\Nfor the Okayama clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.43,0:34:25.23,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Marouji, the assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.97,0:34:29.27,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your weapon?\NHave you a dagger hidden somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.22,0:34:46.45,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Jujitsu, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.69,0:34:49.45,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui-style martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.79,0:34:51.78,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.86,0:34:55.46,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the third assassin sent by them,\Nand by far the most intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.03,0:35:26.93,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you married, Marouji?\NAny children?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.70,0:35:29.13,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.77,0:35:31.96,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.04,0:35:35.23,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She just turned three this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.31,0:35:37.77,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to grow up\Ninto a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.84,0:35:41.04,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. That's something\Nto look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.11,0:35:42.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.01,0:35:47.11,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going to cry for me\Nwhen I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.50,0:36:07.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.01,0:36:10.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughter's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.89,0:36:31.29,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.36,0:36:34.80,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an inn near the Suwa Shrine\Nthat's run by a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.86,0:36:37.73,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hide there for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.00,0:36:40.97,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.43,0:37:07.69,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. It seems a little early\Nfor the festival of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.76,0:37:10.32,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The lanterns will soon be carrying\NYOUR spirit to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.51,0:37:21.47,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the gateway to hell,\Nthe River Styx.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.55,0:37:26.01,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kagairo, a Seki Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.31,0:39:08.25,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanterns to greet the spirits,\Nlanterns to carry them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.32,0:39:10.29,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,In hell, there's nothing\Nbut darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.03,0:39:18.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.83,0:39:29.10,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it at this hour?\NWe're closed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.61,0:39:33.30,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's you, Shuranosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.04,0:39:37.04,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me\Nyou were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.11,0:39:40.08,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look.\NYou're all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.85,0:39:44.25,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.32,0:39:45.95,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.52,0:39:48.62,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!\NHow old is she, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.69,0:39:51.92,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how to hurt\Na girl's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.50,0:39:55.90,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Come in, young lady!\NYou're very welcome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.90,0:40:02.43,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute you think he likes you,\Nand the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.51,0:40:06.27,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And to think I believed him\Nwhen he said he preferred older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.24,0:40:08.23,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.44,0:40:38.46,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.32,0:40:50.81,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep.\NPlease, let me hold you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.10,0:41:04.96,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.03,0:41:09.03,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a very warm person.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.11,0:41:11.04,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.11,0:41:13.80,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,and my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.95,0:41:20.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a man like that be "warm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.38,0:41:22.68,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.86,0:41:28.79,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.14,0:41:40.93,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.09,0:42:03.65,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Mayu!\NYou're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.73,0:42:06.59,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Princess Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.21,0:42:23.20,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.51,0:42:27.18,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the rest of your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.85,0:42:30.12,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. You have earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.16,0:42:35.22,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Words aren't enough\Nto express our appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.29,0:42:38.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. The money is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.73,0:42:42.42,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.03,0:42:45.90,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Sakaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.97,0:42:50.41,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,we must ask you\Nfor just one more favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.97,0:42:52.10,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.18,0:42:55.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must give your life for us...\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.68,0:42:58.15,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.69,0:43:09.16,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you want my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.23,0:43:11.85,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.93,0:43:14.09,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to take\Nyour head with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.10,0:43:18.86,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.94,0:43:21.87,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm dressed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.94,0:43:27.47,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect the Nakura clan,\NI'd give up my wretched life any day!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.45,0:43:32.31,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.72,0:43:41.35,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, men, shoot us both!\NThrough the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.79,0:43:45.12,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop!\N- Princess Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.19,0:43:47.69,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.73,0:43:53.03,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Daizen! What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.60,0:43:57.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki saved my life!\NI will not allow such absurdity!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.27,0:44:01.37,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, this is for the good\Nof our clan! Please understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.44,0:44:03.17,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.25,0:44:05.94,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes against\Nall human decency!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.02,0:44:07.28,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.35,0:44:08.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.49,0:44:13.68,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you will have to kill ME first!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.66,0:44:23.10,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Princess Mayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.17,0:44:26.30,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her to her room!\NAnd call the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.58,0:44:39.11,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your guns down! Go!\NYou're not needed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.36,0:44:56.56,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.84,0:45:04.17,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.61,0:45:09.44,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw a stone at a stray dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.51,0:45:11.98,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll never\Ntake food from you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.05,0:45:13.64,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.49,0:45:27.12,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.48,0:45:47.24,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.82,0:45:51.38,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the white tiger\Nhas been slain.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.45,0:45:54.39,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,One of god's four incarnates\Nhas been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.47,0:46:04.49,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it.\NIt's an ordeal we must undergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.57,0:46:07.33,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a test to see whether\Nthe Tokugawa will rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.40,0:46:09.87,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,for generations to come,\Nor be overthrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.54,0:46:14.37,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all a test!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.97,0:46:36.40,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.94,0:46:45.13,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, sir,\Nbut it's bad. Really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.91,0:46:48.07,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.68,0:46:51.27,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.35,0:46:55.11,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell it from a mile away.\NYeah, you stink of blood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.55,0:47:02.75,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I stink of blood too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.83,0:47:04.26,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.90,0:47:12.66,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find a place to die.\NPretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.87,0:47:17.13,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.24,0:47:21.34,ssp-Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can we do?
